headline: ecobee Expands SmartBuildings Platform with New Multifamily API, Enhancing Flexibility and Control for Property Operators
summary: Today at the AHR Expo, ecobee announced an expansion to its SmartBuildings platform, offering a new SmartBuildings API for multifamily operators. The update gives property managers increased flexibility in how they manage HVAC performance across their portfolios and how ecobee thermostats integrate with existing Resident Experience Platforms (REPs) and building management systems.
